{"body":"## Bug Description

The Dashboard's "Next Action" section shows Morning Reflection at 8:45pm Eastern time, even though it's evening. The user can start it, but it doesn't make sense contextually.

## User Configuration

In Settings, the user has enabled:
- Morning Reflection
- Daily Check-in
- Evening CBT Review

## Expected Behavior

At 8:45pm, the Next Action should show "Evening CBT Review" (or Daily Check-in if not completed), not Morning Reflection.

## Actual Behavior

Morning Reflection is displayed as the Next Action despite it being evening.

## Investigation Areas

- Check time-based task scheduling logic in DashboardPage.vue
- Verify timezone handling (user is in Eastern time)
- Review the `getTaskTimeStatus` function and task prioritization logic","comments":[],"labels":[],"title":"Dashboard shows Morning Reflection as Next Action in the evening"}

